<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. بِتَجْوِيدِ تَرْتِيلِ وَحِفْظِ مَرَاتِبِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَمِنْهُمْ رِجَالٌ فَسَّرُوهُ بِعِلْمِهِمْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَهُمْ عَلَّمُونَا مَا بِهِ مِنْ غَرَائِبِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَمِنْهُمْ رِجَالٌ بِالْحَدِيثِ تَوَلَّعُوا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَمَا كَانَ فِيهِ مِنْ صَحِيحٍ وَذَاهِبِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَمِنْهُمْ رِجَالٌ مُخْلِصُونَ لِرَبِّهِمْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>بِأَنْفُسِهِمْ خُصْبُ الْبِلادِ الأَجَادِبِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَمِنْهُمْ رِجَالٌ يُهْتَدَى بِعِظَاتِهِمْ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>قِيَامٌ إِلَى دِينِ مِنَ اللهِ وَاصِبِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>عَلَى اللهِ رَبِّ النَّاسِ حُسْنُ جَزَاءِهِمْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>بِمَا لا يُوَافِي عَدُّهُ ذِهْنَ حَاسِبِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَمَنْ شَاءَ فَلْيَذْكُرْ جَمَالَ بُثَيْنَةٍ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَمَنْ شَاءَ فَلْيَغْزِلْ بِحُبِّ الرَّبَائِبِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>سَأَذْكُرُ حُبِّي لِلْحَبِيبِ مُحَمَّدٍ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>إِذَا وَصَفُ الْعُشَّاقِ حُبَّ الْحَبَائِبِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَيَبْدُو مُحَيَّاهُ لِعَيْنِي فِي الْكَرَى<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>بِنَفْسِي أَفْدِيهِ إِذَا وَالأَقَارِبِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَتُدْرِكُنِي فِي ذِكْرِهِ قَشْعَرِيرَةٌ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>مِنَ الْوِجْدِ لا يَحْوِيهِ عِلْمُ الأَجَانِبِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَأُلْفِي لِرُوحِي عِنْدَ ذَلِكَ هَزَّةً<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَأُنْسًا وَرَوْحًا فِيهِ وَثْبَةُ وَاثِبِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>